data.description: Great split bedroom floor plan, all one level. Updated kitchen with tile back splash and solid surface countertops. Stainless appliances side by side refrigerator included. Washer and dryer included also. Living room dining area all wood type flooring. Master with walk in closet. Fully fenced yard and space for RV parking. Photos coming 11/29/2023.
